**What is a Cluster Role?**
A ClusterRole contains rules that represent a set of permissions. Permissions are purely additive (there are no "deny" rules).
A ClusterRole is a global concept in the cluster and can be utilised across namespaces.
A Role is the namespaced version of ClusterRole.

